          "reviewBody": "The diverse and inclusive atmosphere is appreciated and the opportunities for extracurricular activities are phenomenal. Also, the dedication of the teachers and staff is commendable. Their attention towards students developmental areas and continuous feedback mechanism to the parents on their children’s strength and  improvement areas are candid. Kudos to the management of the School for its endless efforts. Our overall experience at BVM Global is great!!",
