          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As parents, we are very delighted to have our children groomed by such well equipped and profound knowledgeable teachers who just not raise children by educating subjects but also values that are required and necessary from time to time\nMuch more , extra curricular activities are part of the curriculum which invokes the spark in every child's dream of competing not only on academics but also on various other perspectives of life\nBeyond that , the school monitors every child's growth personally and individual attentiveness is a wonderful aspect\n\nLastly, the school is very safe and right from every staff from the administrative side untill the last person is very friendly and easily approachable by parents\n\nwe will suggest BVm school for all kith and kin who would want to pursue their dreams to come to reality\nHats off !!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
