          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter is now studying UKG.\nWhen we were searching for school for my kid, we had shortlisted 4-5 schools like anybody else.We first visited BVM to know about .We liked the curriculum(especially no exam,no home work policy till class 5) of the school so we decided to admit in BVM itself.\nRight from day one they are doing great job as we expected.Special mention to Priyanka Mam for taking care very well in LKG and Sowkarthiga Mam in UKG.\nTo mention about the academic efficiency,My kid is able to do the basic mathematics like (+/-/*/÷) and able to read, write,understand and converse in English well.Her logical understanding is also good.They teach kids everything through concepts and real life scenarios.\n\nI strongly recommend BVM !",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
